item.title: CVE-2023-30900|2024-08-02T14:37:15.530Z -- siemens -- xpedition%20layout%20browser
item.description: A vulnerability has been identified in Xpedition Layout Browser (All versions < VX.2.14). Affected application contains a stack overflow vulnerability when parsing a PCB file. An attacker can leverage this vulnerability to execute code in the context of the current process.
